data.text: Israel, goe gi manawa lamalia, idimaa go Mee dela ne hai goe.
Goodou gaalege hagaamuina di ingoo o Maa.
Dimaadua e manawa tene gi ana daangada.
Nia daangada a God la gi tenetene idimaa ginaadou gu aali,
Digaula gii wwolo gi nua ma ga hagaamu a God,
e hagamagedaa nia henua ge e daaligi nia daangada,
e lawalawa nia king digaula gi nia daula baalanga,
e daaligi nia henua llauehe gii hai be di hai dela gu haga noho go God.
